    "content": "Discussion is an opportunity for students to make their ideas known and engage in discourse that can help support their developing ideas. Using the following questions in the discussion will help prepare students to generate ideas for their Summary Tables. \n\nSome suggested discussion questions:\n\n* How can we use one plate boundary to make predictions about other plate boundaries?\n\n* What kind of evidence do you need to determine what kind of plate boundary is at a particular location?\n\n* How do plates work as a system?",
